@node "Encounter_at_Farpoint" "Encounter at Farpoint"

                               Episode #721
                            @{b}@{i}ENCOUNTER AT FARPOINT @{ub}@{ui}
                       @{fg fill}D.C. Fontana & Gene Roddenberry@{fg text}
                           @{fg shine}Aired Week of 09/28/87@{fg text}
                            Director: Corey Allen

  In the series opener, the crew of the Enterprise is put on trial by a
 mysterious force called "Q" for all the crimes of mankind.

 @{fg fill}GUEST CAST
 ==========@{fg text}

 Q...John de Lancie                              Zorn...Michael Bell

 * This episode was later split into two episodes and numbered 101 and 102.

 @{" Episode Pic " system "rx trekguide:Trx/Pics.rexx 101 V Encounter_at_Farpoint"}

