@node "Where_None_Has_Gone_Before" "Where None Has Gone Before"

                                Episode #106
                         @{b}@{i}WHERE NONE HAS GONE BEFORE @{ub}@{ui}
                        @{fg fill}Diane Duane & Michael Reaves@{fg text}
                           @{fg shine}Aired Week of 10/26/87@{fg text}
                            Director: Rob Bowman

  The Enterprise and crew travel to unchartered territory when a test on the
 ship's propulsion system backfires and blasts the Enterprise more than a
 billion light years from their own galaxy. This marks the first appearence
 of the traveler.

 @{fg fill}GUEST CAST
 ==========@{fg text}

 Kosinski...Stanley Kamel                        Traveler...Eric Menyuk
 Mother Picard...Herta Ware                      Argyle...Biff Yeager


