@node "We'll_Always_Have_Paris" "We'll Always Have Paris"

                                Episode #124
                           @{b}@{i}WE'LL ALWAYS HAVE PARIS @{ub}@{ui}
                @{fg fill}Deborah Dean Davis & Hannah Louise Shearer@{fg text}
                           @{fg shine}Aired Week of 05/02/88@{fg text}
                          Director: Robert Becker

  While traveling to Sarona Eight for shore leave, the crew experiences
 a bizarre phenomenon in which a moment in time repeats itself. Shortly 
 thereafter, the ship receives a distress call from Vandor Four, where
 Dr. Paul Manheim has been conducting experiments in non-linear time.

 @{fg fill}GUEST CAST
 ==========@{fg text}

